Create Near
Remove Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPStore gmail-remote
    Host imap.gmail.com
    User sarg@sarg.org.ru
    PassCmd "oama access sarg@sarg.org.ru"
    AuthMechs XOAUTH2
    TLSType IMAPS
    TLSVersions +1.3
    CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore gmail-local
    # The trailing "/" is important
    Path ~/.mail/gmail/
    Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox

# https://unix.stackexchange.com/questions/748054/is-it-possible-to-ignore-inbox-folder-when-using-imap-mbsync
# Channel gmail-default
#     Far :gmail-remote:
#     Near :gmail-local:
#     Patterns INBOX

Channel gmail-sent
    Far :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
    Near :gmail-local:sent

Channel gmail-trash
    Far :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Bin"
    Near :gmail-local:trash

Channel gmail-archive
    Far :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/All Mail"
    Near :gmail-local:all

Channel gmail-drafts
    Far :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Drafts"
    Near :gmail-local:drafts

Group gmail
Channel gmail-trash
Channel gmail-drafts
Channel gmail-archive
Channel gmail-sent

